Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.36,0:00:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以买肉包子给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.37,0:00:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别靠那么近 热死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很烫呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.94,0:00:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.04,0:00:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感冒感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要买肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不买
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.51,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.69,0:01:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.56,0:01:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.74,0:01:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.83,0:01:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.24,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 现在吃的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就吃不下秋子阿姨煮的饭了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…买其它的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.07,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 等我一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吃的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「冬天的烟火」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是买更贵的东西就好了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 不要再掉下来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个很难用嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 你应该会用筷子吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道为什么手好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿汤匙给你用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨\N这样未免太宠她了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 这里是水濑家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 突然就倒了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 那就拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以过去看诊的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫出租车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.34,0:04:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一你去待在真琴的身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 现在去医…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴她…不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋\N病成那样要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方做什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我讨厌医生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不去看医生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来治得好的病也会治不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.83,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…不要带我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会再做你讨厌的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再跟\N这个女孩有任何牵扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她将必定会带给你\N无止境的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个陌生人说这种话\N一点根据都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来将会看到真正的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状况怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经稳定下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早饭要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.73,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该没睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天由我来照顾真琴好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道昨晚你说的话的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…天野美汐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于真琴她的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你干嘛说那种话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你知道吗？那个女孩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但那家伙说过\N她对我有所怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N那是有什么地方搞错了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那女孩子…\N曾经相会过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个时候\N她还没有化为人的姿态…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在…说什么啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 你们所在的\N「眺望之丘」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.04,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说从以前\N就住着不可思议的生物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过长时间的岁月\N获得妖力的狐狸们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被视为让村子招致灾祸的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来\N便一直遭到人们的厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是传说吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了带给你灾难而出现的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟说她并不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟说她是给人带来灾祸的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请先记得这句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们为了化为人的姿态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要两个必要的代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代价？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记忆跟…性命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.80,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 你到底是谁啊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…做了一个梦呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在昨晚去的山丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤零零的一个人在等着的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么很悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且对那个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感到非常非常的不可原谅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人让你一个人\N孤零零的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,念那个给我听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱总是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我还小的时候\N捡到的那只小狐狸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为误入陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而受了很重的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照顾它\N让它恢复到能跑为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果说\N现在在这里的真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是它所转世的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样离谱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全不会相信的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会来接你的\N所以到那时候再见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要听…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都已经流汗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.72,0:10:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？没办法弄开钮扣吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我只是不想相信而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.53,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天开始\N真琴的情况一天比一天恶化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.43,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你\N只是在那一瞬间的奇迹里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.91,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那只是那个女孩\N生命回归之时握在手上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间耀眼的光芒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.05,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的确一天比一天的衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像\N回到小孩子的时候一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了很多的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很接近结束的那一刻了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.63,0:12:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 难道\N没有帮助她的方法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.03,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还缩短自己的寿命来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为了什么来见我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了找我报仇吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那么的憎恨我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是因为很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人孤零零的被遗弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想跟相泽你相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这种思念\N才使得奇迹发生的不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们\N并不像传说所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被怨恨嫌恶的存在的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为她们真的是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以别离\N才让人如此的痛苦…悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.51,0:13:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 难道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想再让谁体会到\N跟我一样的悲伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 我向你道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽可能的\N完成那女孩的心愿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.97,0:13:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入二月后 下了第一次的大雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.91,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴渐渐的\N甚至连话都不会说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此\N但是我念漫画给她听时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也会露出高兴的表情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果买了肉包回来…\N也会很高兴的吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支撑着我的内心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经是睡觉的时间了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我不要走吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会待你你身边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一个梦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是淡桃色的棉花糖一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最甜美最美妙的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在放入口中的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.93,0:14:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦就像是被施了魔法般\N虚幻的溶化…消逝了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.07,0:14:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后所剩下的\N就是痛苦的回忆…而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精密检查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大学的医院介绍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是医术非常厉害的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要给他们看\N一定会好起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.88,0:14:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌医生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你不要带我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有一个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.26,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这种地方好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.97,0:15:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是去什么很高级的地方的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太紧张\N不就没有一家人的感觉了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.11,0:15:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.28,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴到现在为止都没有什么生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.45,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就是真琴的生日\N对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 这样子也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐\N真琴 很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 为了纪念生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去拍那个吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴你在干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起来拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.47,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 要拍啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被烫到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴真的很喜欢烟火呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.82,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的隆冬中的烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.79,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注视着微微的烟火的\N真琴的侧脸也会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会有如仙女棒一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面临稍纵即逝的命运吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔天早上 真琴又发了高烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这代表着什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有着切身之痛的了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在救护车已经要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 该准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.07,0:17:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴\N有没有什么想做的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要去哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要去那个山丘吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到眺望之丘去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴是病人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不早点带去给医生看的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生是治不好真琴的病的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回她出生的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生的地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眺望之丘吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她的伙伴在等着她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我以前捡到的狐狸\N转世而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.41,0:18:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢你…妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.17,0:19:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一以前捡到的小狐狸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它很喜欢铃铛的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.94,0:19:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子总是在玩\N我钱包上面的铃铛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到那里去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那个山丘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.20,0:19:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫天野美汐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.42,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 是个好名字喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 不要睡着了\N就快要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摇看看吧 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢的铃铛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让它响看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让它多响几声看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗？\N是你出生的地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天…天气变暖和之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一定会恢复的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 到时候再一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 你怎么了 真琴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经到眺望之丘了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还太早了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.12,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不错的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天野说话还是像个老太婆一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请说我言行举止文雅好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回想起一件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我初恋情人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经对它说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个叫做泽渡真琴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.96,0:21:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个多么温柔又漂亮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然记得这一件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是\N指引你们两个人的路标呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.21,0:21:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想\N它们仍然还会在草原上奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那小小的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会有新的生命诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…成长着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循环不息的生命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.21,0:22:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从随风飘流的云朵之间\N窥视到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.15,0:22:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连熟悉的街道也闪闪发光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.33,0:22:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.83,0:22:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.71,0:23:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真来盖过溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.19,0:23:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间静悄悄的流动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.19,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂着温柔的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.80,0:23:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为冻僵的思念也会化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么愿望都会实现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给她的玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前小小的玩偶
